4 A BILL
5 TO BE ENTITLED
6 AN ACT
7
8
9 Relating to Barbour County; to amend Section 45-3-60,
10 Code of Alabama 1975, to further provide for the coroner's
11 mileage rate.
12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA:
13 Section 1. Section 45-3-60, Code of Alabama 1975, is
14 amended to read as follows:
15 "§45-3-60
16 In addition to any compensation or expense allowance
17 now provided by Section 12-19-192, the Coroner of Barbour
18 County shall receive an expense allowance and mileage to be
19 set by the county commission by resolution not to exceed four
20 hundred dollars ($400) a month expense allowance and fifty
21 cents ($.50) per mile a mileage reimbursement rate equal to
22 the Internal Revenue Service's business use rate, to be paid
23 from the county general fund."
24 Section 2. This act shall become effective on October
25 1, 2026.
